            <title>[SPARK-23425] load data for hdfs file path with wild card usage is not working properly</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-23425</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;load data command&#160; for loading data from non local&#160; file paths by using wild card strings lke * are not working&lt;/p&gt;

